[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Examples of such material inciting hatred and murder online[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]a.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal] 
[normal]www.madni.org/Qadiani/difference.htm
[normal]On this website it describes three types of “disbelievers”. Subsequently (extracted below) it is explained that 
[normal]Muslims should kill an apostate
[normal]. It is further explained in the last screen shot that 
[normal]Ahmadi Muslims
[normal] referred to as Qadianis are the third type of disbelievers and they 
[normal]should also be killed
[normal]. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]b.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]http://www.paklinks.com/gs/all-views/405097-qadiani-ahmadi-population-in-pakistan-globally.html
[normal]This is an example of a blogging site where it shows that 
[normal]it 
[normal]is now widely known among online users that Ahmadi Muslims should be killed.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]c.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]http://irshad.org/exposed/fatwas/edesai.php
[normal] and 
[normal]http://irshad.org/brochures/message.php
[normal]Inciting hatred and calling for a social boycott of A
[normal]hmadi Muslims
