[normal]&#xa0;[bold]Conclusion[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]a.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Establish a statutory regulatory body (such as 
[normal]Ofcom
[normal]) to investigate and take measures 
[normal]and sanctions against those promoting such material online
[normal] (or extend Ofcom’s powers to cover this function as well);
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]b.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Establish a non-statutory body (such as the Internet Watch Foundation (IWF)) to investigate such material online, and notify ISPs to take
[normal] 
[normal]measures against such websites;
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]c.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Place a statutory obligation on ISPs to take action against websites disseminating such material online.
